@model CoreCodeCamp.Models.Emails.TalkModel
@{
  Layout = "Emails/_Layout";
}
<h2>@Model.Talk.Speaker.Event.Name Session Acceptance</h2>
<br />
<p>Hello @Model.Talk.Speaker.Name,</p>
<p>
  Thank you for your session submission(s) to @Model.Talk.Speaker.Event.Name. We're pleased to
  inform you that the following submission has been accepted.
  Final session rooms and schedule will be published as soon as
  possible.  Please visit http://atlantacodecamp.com for more details.
</p>

<h3>@Model.Talk.Title</h3>

<div>PLEASE CONFIRM YOUR SESSION by replying to this email or emailing codecamp@live.com.</div> 

<div>PLEASE REGISTER @@ http://www.eventbrite.com/e/@Model.Talk.Speaker.Event.RegistrationLink 
  by @Model.Talk.Speaker.Event.CallForSpeakersClosed.ToShortDateString() using the following speaker code.</div>
<ul><li>Speaker Code: ACC@(Model.Moniker)-Speaker</li></ul>
<p>In addition to your session acceptance, here are some important reminders.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Session length is 60 minutes.  Please ensure your sessions allow for approximately 10 minutes of Q&A as needed.</li>
  <li>Speaker Dinner Friday, September 13th. We will be hosting a Speaker Dinner on Friday evening, September 13th. We would love for you to join us and meet your fellow speakers.</li>
</ul>
<p>We have a great list of speakers and we are thrilled to have you participating in Atlanta Code Camp @(Model.Moniker). Thank you for your participation and congratulations on your session acceptance!</p>
<br />
<br />
We'd appreciate it if you helped get the word out about the event. You can point people at the main website at:

<h4>http://atlantacodecamp.com</h4>

Alternatively, you can point them to your speaker page that will include your talk(s):
<h4>http://atlantacodecamp.com/@(Model.Moniker)/speakers/@Model.Talk.Speaker.Slug</h4>
<br />
<br />
<div>Regards,</div>
<div>Atlanta Code Camp Planning Committee</div>
<div>codecamp@live.com</div>
<div>Developers Association of Georgia</div>
